V</a></i>\n</td>\n<td>\u00a513,000\n</td>\n<td>2010 August\n</td>\n<td>Resin-cast conversion kit for MG-129.\n</td></tr></tbody></table><p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p></div><div class=\"wds-tab__content\"><p class=\"mw-empty-elt\">\n</p><table class=\"wikitable sortable\">\n<tbody><tr>\n<th>MG #\n</th>\n<th>Model\n</th>\n<th>Series\n</th>\n<th>Yen Price\n</th>\n<th>Announcement Date\n</th>\n<th>Notes\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>N/A\n</td>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/GF13-011NC_Dragon_Gundam\" title=\"GF13-011NC Dragon Gundam\">GF13-011NC Dragon Gundam</a>\n</td>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/Mobile_Fighter_G_Gundam\" title=\"Mobile Fighter G Gundam\">Mobile Fighter G Gundam</a>\n</td>\n<td>\u00a5\n</td>\n<td>2002 May\n</td>\n<td>Originally announced at the 41st Shizuoka Hobby Show 2002, with the prototype model on display at the event. Plans to release this model never went beyond this announcement.\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>N/A\n</td>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/GF13-006NA_Gundam_Maxter\" title=\"GF13-006NA Gundam Maxter\">GF13-006NA Gundam Maxter</a>\n</td>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/Mobile_Fighter_G_Gundam\" title=\"Mobile Fighter G Gundam\">Mobile Fighter G Gundam</a>\n</td>\n<td>\u00a5\n</td>\n<td>2002 May\n</td>\n<td>Originally announced at the 41st Shizuoka Hobby Show 2002, with the prototype model on display at the event. Plans to release this model never went beyond this announcement.\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>N/A\n</td>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/GF13-050NSW_Nobel_Gundam\" title=\"GF13-050NSW Nobel Gundam\">GF13-050NSW Nobel Gundam</a>\n</td>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/Mobile_Fighter_G_Gundam\" title=\"Mobile Fighter G Gundam\">Mobile Fighter G Gundam</a>\n</td>\n<td>\u00a5\n</td>\n<td>2002 May\n</td>\n<td>Originally announced at the 41st Shizuoka Hobby Show 2002, with the prototype model on display at the event. Plans to release this model never went beyond this announcement.\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>N/A\n</td>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/JMF1336R_Rising_Gundam\" title=\"JMF1336R Rising Gundam\">JMF1336R Rising Gundam</a>\n</td>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/Mobile_Fighter_G_Gundam\" title=\"Mobile Fighter G Gundam\">Mobile Fighter G Gundam</a>\n</td>\n<td>\u00a5\n</td>\n<td>2002 May\n</td>\n<td>Parts variant of MG-049. Originally announced at the 41st Shizuoka Hobby Show 2002, with the prototype model on display at the event. Plans to release this model never went beyond this announcement.\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>N/A\n</td>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/PF-78-1_Perfect_Gundam\" title=\"PF-78-1 Perfect Gundam\">PF-78-1 Perfect Gundam</a> (Katsumi Kawaguchi Produce Version)\n</td>\n<td><i><a href=\"/wiki/Plamo-Kyoshiro\" title=\"Plamo-Kyoshiro\">Plamo-Kyoshiro</a></i>\n</td>\n<td>\u00a5\n</td>\n<td>2004 May\n</td>\n<td>Color variant of MG-067. Originally announced at the 43rd Shizuoka Hobby Show 2004, with the prototype model on display at the event. Plans to release this model never went beyond this announcement.\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>N/A\n</td>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/F90_Gundam_F90\" title=\"F90 Gundam F90\">F90 Gundam F90</a>\n</td>\n<td><i><a href=\"/wiki/Mobile_Suit_Gundam_F90\" title=\"Mobile Suit Gundam F90\">Mobile Suit Gundam F90</a></i>\n</td>\n<td>\u00a5\n</td>\n<td>2006 May\n</td>\n<td>Development announced at the 45th Shizuoka Hobby Show 2006, with a modified version of the original <a href=\"/wiki/1/100_Gundam_F90_Model_Series\" title=\"1/100 Gundam F90 Model Series\">1990 Gundam F90 kit</a> displayed as a prototype.<sup id=\"cite_ref-6\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-6\"><span class=\"cite-bracket\">&#91;</span>6<span class=\"cite-bracket\">&#93;</span></a></sup> Plans for this kit did not go beyond this announcement. A new MG kit was released in August 2019 as a P-Bandai exclusive after the release of MG-203.\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>N/A\n</td>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/MS-06V_Zaku_Tank\" title=\"MS-06V Zaku Tank\">MS-06V Zaku Tank</a>\n</td>\n<td><i><a href=\"/wiki/Mobile_Suit_Variation\" title=\"Mobile Suit Variation\">Mobile Suit Variation</a></i>\n</td>\n<td>\u00a5\n</td>\n<td>2008 May\n</td>\n<td>Tentative release announced at the 47th Shizuoka Hobby Show 2008 with the prototype model on display.<sup id=\"cite_ref-7\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-7\"><span class=\"cite-bracket\">&#91;</span>7<span class=\"cite-bracket\">&#93;</span></a></sup> Plans to release this model never went beyond this announcement\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>N/A\n</td>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/GN-001_Gundam_Exia\" title=\"GN-001 Gundam Exia\">GN-001 Gundam Exia</a> Roll Out Color\n</td>\n<td><i><a href=\"/wiki/Mobile_Suit_Gundam_00\" title=\"Mobile Suit Gundam 00\">Mobile Suit Gundam 00</a></i>\n</td>\n<td>\u00a5\n</td>\n<td>2009 August\n</td>\n<td>Color variant of MG-123. Originally announced at Gunpla Big Expo Tokyo 2009 as a Bandai Hobby Online Shop exclusive, with the prototype model on display.<sup id=\"cite_ref-8\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-8\"><span class=\"cite-bracket\">&#91;</span>8<span class=\"cite-bracket\">&#93;</span></a></sup> Plans to release this model never went beyond this announcement.\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>N/A\n</td>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/MSN-04II_Nightingale\" title=\"MSN-04II Nightingale\">MSN-04II Nightingale</a>\n</td>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/Mobile_Suit_Gundam:_Char%27s_Counterattack_-_Beltorchika%27s_Children\" title=\"Mobile Suit Gundam: Char&#39;s Counterattack - Beltorchika&#39;s Children\">Mobile Suit Gundam: Char's Counterattack - Beltorchika's Children</a>\n</td>\n<td>\u00a5\n</td>\n<td>2010\n</td>\n<td>Originally announced at Gunpla Expo World Tour 2010 Japan, with the prototype model on display at the event. Plans to release this model were canceled, but it resurfaced in 2014 as the first <a href=\"/wiki/Reborn-One_Hundred\" title=\"Reborn-One Hundred\">Reborn-One Hundred</a> kit.\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>N/A\n</td>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/GNX-803T_GN-XIV\" title=\"GNX-803T GN-XIV\">GNX-803T GN-XIV</a>\n</td>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/Mobile_Suit_Gundam_00_The_Movie_-A_wakening_of_the_Trailblazer-\" title=\"Mobile Suit Gundam 00 The Movie -A wakening of the Trailblazer-\">Mobile Suit Gundam 00 The Movie -A wakening of the Trailblazer-</a>\n</td>\n<td>\u00a5\n</td>\n<td>2010 October\n</td>\n<td>Parts and color variant of MG-129. Tentative release announced at the 50th All Japan Plamodel Hobby Show 2010, with the prototype model on display.<sup id=\"cite_ref-9\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-9\"><span class=\"cite-bracket\">&#91;</span>9<span class=\"cite-bracket\">&#93;</span></a></sup> Plans to release this model never went beyond this announcement.\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>N/A\n</td>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/AGE-3_Gundam_AGE-3_Normal\" title=\"AGE-3 Gundam AGE-3 Normal\">AGE-3 Gundam AGE-3 Normal</a>\n</td>\n<td><i><a href=\"/wiki/Mobile_Suit_Gundam_AGE\" title=\"Mobile Suit Gundam AGE\">Mobile Suit Gundam AGE</a></i>\n</td>\n<td>\u00a5\n</td>\n<td>2012 November\n</td>\n<td>Tentative release announced at Gunpla Expo World Tour 2012 Japan, with the prototype model on display at the event.<sup id=\"cite_ref-MG_AGE_10-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-MG_AGE-10\"><span class=\"cite-bracket\">&#91;</span>10<span class=\"cite-bracket\">&#93;</span></a></sup> Plans to release this model never went beyond this announcement.\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>N/A\n</td>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/AGE-FX_Gundam_AGE-FX\" title=\"AGE-FX Gundam AGE-FX\">AGE-FX Gundam AGE-FX</a>\n</td>\n<td><i><a href=\"/wiki/Mobile_Suit_Gundam_AGE\" title=\"Mobile Suit Gundam AGE\">Mobile Suit Gundam AGE</a></i>\n</td>\n<td>\u00a5\n</td>\n<td>2012 November\n</td>\n<td>Tentative release announced at Gunpla Expo World Tour 2012 Japan, with the prototype model on display at the event.<sup id=\"cite_ref-MG_AGE_10-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-MG_AGE-10\"><span class=\"cite-bracket\">&#91;</span>10<span class=\"cite-bracket\">&#93;</span></a></sup> Plans to release this model never went beyond this announcement.\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>N/A\n</td>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/Ovv-f_Gafran\" title=\"Ovv-f Gafran\">Ovv-f Gafran</a>\n</td>\n<td><i><a href=\"/wiki/Mobile_Suit_Gundam_AGE\" title=\"Mobile Suit Gundam AGE\">Mobile Suit Gundam AGE</a></i>\n</td>\n<td>\u00a5\n</td>\n<td>2012 November\n</td>\n<td>Originally announced at Gunpla Expo World Tour 2012 Japan, with a tentative roll out date of April 2012.<sup id=\"cite_ref-11\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-11\"><span class=\"cite-bracket\">&#91;</span>11<span class=\"cite-bracket\">&#93;</span></a></sup> Plans to release this model never went beyond this announcement.\n</td></tr></tbody></table><p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p></div></div><p>Yen price excluding 5% tax (8% from 2014 to 2019; 10% from 2019 October onwards).\n</p><h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Special_Editions\">Special Editions</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a title=\"Sign in to edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" data-tracking-label=\"log-in-edit-section\" data-action=\"edit-section\" href=\"https://auth.fandom.com/signin?redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fgundam.fandom.com%2Fwiki%2FMaster_Grade%3Fveaction%3Dedit%26section%3D2&amp;uselang=en&amp;metadata=article-registration-edit-article-section\" data-testid=\"log-in-edit-section\" aria-label=\"Sign in to edit\"><svg class=\"wds-icon wds-icon-tiny\" aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\"><use xlink:href=\"#wds-icons-pencil-tiny\"></use></svg></a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"tabber wds-tabber\"><div class=\"wds-tabs__wrapper with-bottom-border\"><ul class=\"wds-tabs\"><li class=\"wds-tabs__tab wds-is-current\" data-hash=\"1996\"><div class=\"wds-tabs__tab-label\"><a href=\"#\">1996</a></div></li><li class=\"wds-tabs__tab\" data-hash=\"1998\"><div class=\"wds-tabs__tab-label\"><a href=\"#\">1998</a></div></li><li class=\"wds-tabs__tab\" data-hash=\"1999\"><div class=\"wds-tabs__tab-label\"><a href=\"#\">1999</a></div></li><li class=\"wds-tabs__tab\" data-hash=\"2000\"><div class=\"wds-tabs__tab-label\"><a href=\"#\">2000</a></div></li><li class=\"wds-tabs__tab\" data-hash=\"2003\"><div class=\"wds-tabs__tab-label\"><a href=\"#\">2003</a></div></li><li class=\"wds-tabs__tab\" data-hash=\"2005\"><div class=\"wds-tabs__tab-label\"><a href=\"#\">2005</a></div></li><li class=\"wds-tabs__tab\" data-hash=\"2006\"><div class=\"wds-tabs__tab-label\"><a href=\"#\">2006</a></div></li><li class=\"wds-tabs__tab\" data-hash=\"2007\"><div class=\"wds-tabs__tab-label\"><a href=\"#\">2007</a></div></li><li class=\"wds-tabs__tab\" data-hash=\"2008\"><div class=\"wds-tabs__tab-label\"><a href=\"#\">2008</a></div></li><li class=\"wds-tabs__tab\" data-hash=\"2009\"><div class=\"wds-tabs__tab-label\"><a href=\"#\">2009</a></div></li><li class=\"wds-tabs__tab\" data-hash=\"2010\"><div class=\"wds-tabs__tab-label\"><a href=\"#\">2010</a></div></li><li class=\"wds-tabs__tab\" data-hash=\"2011\"><div class=\"wds-tabs__tab-label\"><a href=\"#\">2011</a></div></li><li class=\"wds-tabs__tab\" data-hash=\"2012\"><div class=\"wds-tabs__tab-label\"><a href=\"#\">2012</a></div></li><li class=\"wds-tabs__tab\" data-hash=\"2013\"><div class=\"wds-tabs__tab-label\"><a href=\"#\">2013</a></div></li><li class=\"wds-tabs__tab\" data-hash=\"2014\"><div class=\"wds-tabs__tab-label\"><a href=\"#\">2014</a></div></li><li class=\"wds-tabs__tab\" data-hash=\"2016\"><div class=\"wds-tabs__tab-label\"><a href=\"#\">2016</a></div></li><li class=\"wds-tabs__tab\" data-hash=\"2017\"><div class=\"wds-tabs__tab-label\"><a href=\"#\">2017</a></div></li><li class=\"wds-tabs__tab\" data-hash=\"2018\"><div class=\"wds-tabs__tab-label\"><a href=\"#\">2018</a></div></li><li class=\"wds-tabs__tab\" data-hash=\"2019\"><div class=\"wds-tabs__tab-label\"><a href=\"#\">2019</a></div></li></ul></div><div class=\"wds-tab__content wds-is-current\"><p class=\"mw-empty-elt\">\n</p><table class=\"wikitable sortable\">\n<tbody><tr>\n<th>MG #\n</th>\n<th>Model\n</th>\n<th>Series\n</th>\n<th>Yen Price\n</th>\n<th>Release Date\n</th>\n<th>Notes\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>N/A <figure class=\"mw-halign-right\" typeof=\"mw:File\"><a href=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/gundam/images/8/81/MG_RX-78-2_Crystal_Ver.jpg/revision/latest?cb=20180829125109\" class=\"mw-file-description image\"><img alt=\"MG RX-78-2 Crystal Ver\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"100\" height=\"149\" class=\"mw-file-element lazyload\" data-image-name=\"MG RX-78-2 Crystal Ver.jpg\" data-image-key=\"MG_RX-78-2_Crystal_Ver.jpg\" data-relevant=\"1\" data-src=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/gundam/images/8/81/MG_RX-78-2_Crystal_Ver.jpg/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/100?cb=20180829125109\" /></a><figcaption></figcaption></figure>\n</td>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/RX-78-2_Gundam\" title=\"RX-78-2 Gundam\">RX-78-2 Gundam</a> Crystal Version\n</td>\n<td><i><a href=\"/wiki/Mobile_Suit_Gundam\" title=\"Mobile Suit Gundam\">Mobile Suit Gundam</a></i>\n</td>\n<td>\u00a52,800\n</td>\n<td>1996 October\n</td>\n<td>Limited clear color variant of MG-001.\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>N/A <figure class=\"mw-halign-right\" typeof=\"mw:File\"><a href=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/gundam/images/c/ce/MG_Char%27s_Zaku_II_Crystal_Ver.jpg/revision/latest?cb=20180829125117\" class=\"mw-file-description image\"><img alt=\"MG Char&#39;s Zaku II Crystal Ver\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"100\" height=\"150\" class=\"mw-file-element lazyload\" data-image-name=\"MG Char&#39;s Zaku II Crystal Ver.jpg\" data-image-key=\"MG_Char%27s_Zaku_II_Crystal_Ver.jpg\" data-relevant=\"1\" data-src=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/gundam/images/c/ce/MG_Char%27s_Zaku_II_Crystal_Ver.jpg/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/100?cb=20180829125117\" /></a><figcaption></figcaption></figure>\n</td>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/MS-06S_Zaku_II_Commander_Type\" title=\"MS-06S Zaku II Commander Type\">MS-06S Zaku II</a> Crystal Version\n</td>\n<td><i><a href=\"/wiki/Mobile_Suit_Gundam\" title=\"Mobile Suit Gundam\">Mobile Suit Gundam</a></i>\n</td>\n<td>\u00a52,800\n</td>\n<td>1996 October\n</td>\n<td>Limited clear color variant of MG-002.\n</td></tr></tbody></table><p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p></div><div class=\"wds-tab__content\"><p class=\"mw-empty-elt\">\n</p><table class=\"wikitable sortable\">\n<tbody><tr>\n<th>MG #\n</th>\n<th>Model\n</th>\n<th>Series\n</th>\n<th>Yen Price\n</th>\n<th>Release Date\n</th>\n<th>Notes\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>N/A <figure class=\"mw-halign-right\" typeof=\"mw:File\"><a href=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/gundam/images/f/f0/MG_Zaku_II_Crystal_Ver.jpg/revision/latest?cb=20180829125124\" class=\"mw-file-description image\"><img alt=\"MG Zaku II Crystal Ver\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"100\" height=\"152\" class=\"mw-file-element lazyload\" data-image-name=\"MG Zaku II Crystal Ver.jpg\" data-image-key=\"MG_Zaku_II_Crystal_Ver.jpg\" data-relevant=\"1\" data-src=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/gundam/images/f/f0/MG_Zaku_II_Crystal_Ver.jpg/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/100?cb=20180829125124\" /></a><figcaption></figcaption></figure>\n</td>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/MS-06F_Zaku_II\" title=\"MS-06F Zaku II\">MS-06F</a>/<a href=\"/wiki/MS-06J_Zaku_II_Ground_Type\" title=\"MS-06J Zaku II Ground Type\">J</a> Zaku II Crystal Version\n</td>\n<td><i><a href=\"/wiki/Mobile_Suit_Gundam\" title=\"Mobile Suit Gundam\">Mobile Suit Gundam</a></i>\n</td>\n<td>\u00a52,800\n</td>\n<td>1998 October\n</td>\n<td>Limited clear color variant of MG-003.\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>N/A <figure class=\"mw-halign-right\" typeof=\"mw:File\"><a href=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/gundam/images/c/c6/MG_RX-78-2_Coating_Ver.jpg/revision/latest?cb=20180829152918\" class=\"mw-file-description image\"><img alt=\"MG RX-78-2 Coating Ver\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"100\" height=\"151\" class=\"mw-file-element lazyload\" data-image-name=\"MG RX-78-2 Coating Ver.jpg\" data-image-key=\"MG_RX-78-2_Coating_Ver.jpg\" data-relevant=\"1\" data-src=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/gundam/images/c/c6/MG_RX-78-2_Coating_Ver.jpg/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/100?cb=20180829152918\" /></a><figcaption></figcaption></figure>\n</td>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/RX-78-2_Gundam\" title=\"RX-78-2 Gundam\">Gundam RX-78-2</a> Coating Version\n</td>\n<td><i><a href=\"/wiki/Mobile_Suit_Gundam\" title=\"Mobile Suit Gundam\">Mobile Suit Gundam</a></i>\n</td>\n<td>\u00a53,500\n</td>\n<td>1998 June\n</td>\n<td>Special chrome color plated variant of MG-001. Includes 1/20 scale <a href=\"/wiki/Amuro_Ray\" title=\"Amuro Ray\">Amuro Ray</a> figure. Released to commemorate the 20th anniversary of <i>Gundam</i>.\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>N/A <figure class=\"mw-halign-right\" typeof=\"mw:File\"><a href=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/gundam/images/f/fe/MG_Zeta_Gundam_Coating_Ver.jpg/revision/latest?cb=20180831200037\" class=\"mw-file-description image\"><img alt=\"MG Zeta Gundam Coating Ver\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"100\" height=\"129\" class=\"mw-file-element lazyload\" data-image-name=\"MG Zeta Gundam Coating Ver.jpg\" data-image-key=\"MG_Zeta_Gundam_Coating_Ver.jpg\" data-relevant=\"1\" data-src=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/gundam/images/f/fe/MG_Zeta_Gundam_Coating_Ver.jpg/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/100?cb=20180831200037\" /></a><figcaption></figcaption></figure>\n</td>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/MSZ-006_Zeta_Gundam\" title=\"MSZ-006 Zeta Gundam\">MSZ-006 Zeta Gundam</a> Coating Version\n</td>\n<td><i><a href=\"/wiki/Mobile_Suit_Zeta_Gundam\" title=\"Mobile Suit Zeta Gundam\">Mobile Suit Zeta Gundam</a></i>\n</td>\n<td>\u00a54,000\n</td>\n<td>1998 July\n</td>\n<td>Special chrome color plated variant of MG-005. Includes 1/20 scale <a href=\"/wiki/Kamille_Bidan\" title=\"Kamille Bidan\">Kamille Bidan</a> figure. Released to commemorate the 20th anniversary of <i>Gundam</i>.\n</td></tr></tbody></table><p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p></div><div class=\"wds-tab__content\"><p class=\"mw-empty-elt\">\n</p><table class=\"wikitable sortable\">\n<tbody><tr>\n<th>MG #\n</th>\n<th>Model\n</th>\n<th>Series\n</th>\n<th>Yen Price\n</th>\n<th>Release Date\n</th>\n<th>Notes\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>N/A <figure class=\"mw-halign-right\" typeof=\"mw:File\"><a href=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/gundam/images/b/bd/MG_Char%27s_Zaku_II_Coating_Ver.jpg/revision/latest?cb=20180829152934\" class=\"mw-file-description image\"><img alt=\"MG Char&#39;s Zaku II Coating Ver\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"100\" height=\"152\" class=\"mw-file-element lazyload\" data-image-name=\"MG Char&#39;s Zaku II Coating Ver.jpg\" data-image-key=\"MG_Char%27s_Zaku_II_Coating_Ver.jpg\" data-relevant=\"1\" data-src=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/gundam/images/b/bd/MG_Char%27s_Zaku_II_Coating_Ver.jpg/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/100?cb=20180829152934\" /></a><figcaption></figcaption></figure>\n</td>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/MS-06S_Zaku_II_Commander_Type\" title=\"MS-06S Zaku II Commander Type\">MS-06S Zaku II</a> Coating Version\n</td>\n<td><i><a href=\"/wiki/Mobile_Suit_Gundam\" title=\"Mobile Suit Gundam\">Mobile Suit Gundam</a></i>\n</td>\n<td>\u00a53,500\n</td>\n<td>1999 August\n</td>\n<td>Special chrome color plated variant of MG-002. Includes 1/20 scale <a href=\"/wiki/Char_Aznable\" title=\"Char Aznable\">Char Aznable</a> figure. Released to commemorate the 20th anniversary of <i>Gundam</i>.\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>N/A <figure class=\"mw-halign-right\" ty