h=\"100\" height=\"158\" class=\"mw-file-element lazyload\" data-image-name=\"MG V2 Gundam Ver.Ka Clear Gold Plated Ver.jpg\" data-image-key=\"MG_V2_Gundam_Ver.Ka_Clear_Gold_Plated_Ver.jpg\" data-relevant=\"1\" data-src=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/gundam/images/9/9e/MG_V2_Gundam_Ver.Ka_Clear_Gold_Plated_Ver.jpg/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/100?cb=20170130143719\" /></a><figcaption></figcaption></figure>\n</td>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/LM314V21_Victory_2_Gundam\" title=\"LM314V21 Victory 2 Gundam\">LM314V21 Victory Two Gundam \"Ver.Ka\"</a> Clear/Gold Plated Ver.\n</td>\n<td><i><a href=\"/wiki/Mobile_Suit_Victory_Gundam\" title=\"Mobile Suit Victory Gundam\">Mobile Suit Victory Gundam</a></i>\n</td>\n<td>\u00a55,000\n</td>\n<td>2016 November\n</td>\n<td>Gunpla Expo World Tour Japan 2016 Winter exclusive clear armor variant of MG-191 with the V-fin and chest and wing parts plated in gold chrome. Includes water slide decal sheet.\n</td>\n<td>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>N/A<figure class=\"mw-halign-right\" typeof=\"mw:File\"><a href=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/gundam/images/3/33/Weapon_Armor_Hanger_for_Full_Armor_Gundam_Thunderbolt.jpg/revision/latest?cb=20180831115735\" class=\"mw-file-description image\"><img alt=\"Weapon Armor Hanger for Full Armor Gundam Thunderbolt\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"100\" height=\"148\" class=\"mw-file-element lazyload\" data-image-name=\"Weapon Armor Hanger for Full Armor Gundam Thunderbolt.jpg\" data-image-key=\"Weapon_Armor_Hanger_for_Full_Armor_Gundam_Thunderbolt.jpg\" data-relevant=\"1\" data-src=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/gundam/images/3/33/Weapon_Armor_Hanger_for_Full_Armor_Gundam_Thunderbolt.jpg/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/100?cb=20180831115735\" /></a><figcaption></figcaption></figure>\n</td>\n<td>Weapon &amp; Armor Hanger for <a href=\"/wiki/FA-78_Full_Armor_Gundam_(Thunderbolt_Ver.)\" 