lity_Type\" title=\"MS-06R-2 Zaku II High Mobility Type\">MS-06R-2 Zaku II (Gabby Hazard Custom)</a>. Includes water slide decal sheet.\n</td>\n<td>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>N/A<figure class=\"mw-halign-right\" typeof=\"mw:File\"><a href=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/gundam/images/0/0c/HWS_Expansion_Set_for_%CE%BD_Gundam_Ver_Ka.jpg/revision/latest?cb=20180831120205\" class=\"mw-file-description image\"><img alt=\"HWS Expansion Set for \u03bd Gundam Ver Ka\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"100\" height=\"64\" class=\"mw-file-element lazyload\" data-image-name=\"HWS Expansion Set for \u03bd Gundam Ver Ka.jpg\" data-image-key=\"HWS_Expansion_Set_for_%CE%BD_Gundam_Ver_Ka.jpg\" data-relevant=\"1\" data-src=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/gundam/images/0/0c/HWS_Expansion_Set_for_%CE%BD_Gundam_Ver_Ka.jpg/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/100?cb=20180831120205\" /></a><figcaption></figcaption></figure>\n</td>\n<td>HWS Expansion Set for <a href=\"/wiki/RX-93_%CE%BD_Gundam\" title=\"RX-93 \u03bd Gundam\">\u03bd Gundam \"Ver.Ka\"</a>\n</td>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/Char%27s_Counterattack_Mobile_Suit_Variations\" title=\"Char&#39;s Counterattack Mobile Suit Variations\">CCA-MSV</a>\n</td>\n<td>\u00a52,400\n</td>\n<td>2016 December\n</td>\n<td>P-Bandai exclusive accessory kit to convert MG-163 into <a href=\"/wiki/FA-93HWS_%CE%BD_Gundam_Heavy_Weapons_System_Type\" title=\"FA-93HWS \u03bd Gundam Heavy Weapons System Type\">FA-93HWS \u03bd Gundam Heavy Weapons System Type</a>. Includes water slide decal sheet.\n</td>\n<td>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>N/A<figure class=\"mw-halign-right\" typeof=\"mw:File\"><a href=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/gundam/images/1/19/MG_%CE%BD_Gundam_HWS_Ver_Ka.jpg/revision/latest?cb=20200207050832\" class=\"mw-file-description image\"><img alt=\"MG \u03bd Gundam HWS Ver Ka\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALA