7/MG_CrossboneGundamX2Custom_VerKa.jpg/revision/latest?cb=20170629132254\" class=\"mw-file-description image\"><img alt=\"MG CrossboneGundamX2Custom VerKa\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"100\" height=\"158\" class=\"mw-file-element lazyload\" data-image-name=\"MG CrossboneGundamX2Custom VerKa.jpg\" data-image-key=\"MG_CrossboneGundamX2Custom_VerKa.jpg\" data-relevant=\"1\" data-src=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/gundam/images/6/67/MG_CrossboneGundamX2Custom_VerKa.jpg/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/100?cb=20170629132254\" /></a><figcaption></figcaption></figure>\n</td>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/XM-X2ex_Crossbone_Gundam_X-2_Kai\" title=\"XM-X2ex Crossbone Gundam X-2 Kai\">XM-X2ex Crossbone Gundam X2 Custom \"Ver.Ka\"</a>\n</td>\n<td><i><a href=\"/wiki/Mobile_Suit_Crossbone_Gundam\" title=\"Mobile Suit Crossbone Gundam\">Mobile Suit Crossbone Gundam</a></i>\n</td>\n<td>\u00a54,400\n</td>\n<td>2017 June\n</td>\n<td>P-Bandai exclusive parts variant of MG XM-X2 Crossbone Gundam X2 \"Ver.Ka\". Includes water slide decal sheet.\n</td>\n<td>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>N/A<figure class=\"mw-halign-right\" typeof=\"mw:File\"><a href=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/gundam/images/5/5f/MG_Zaku_II_%28Shin_Matsunaga_Custom%29.jpg/revision/latest?cb=20180831121543\" class=\"mw-file-description image\"><img alt=\"MG Zaku II (Shin Matsunaga Custom)\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"100\" height=\"126\" class=\"mw-file-element lazyload\" data-image-name=\"MG Zaku II (Shin Matsunaga Custom).jpg\" data-image-key=\"MG_Zaku_II_%28Shin_Matsunaga_Custom%29.jpg\" data-relevant=\"1\" data-src=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/gundam/images/5/5f/MG_Zaku_II_%28Shin_Matsunaga_Custom%29.jpg/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/100?cb=20180831121543\" /></a><figcaption></figcaptio