m_Perfectibility.jpg/revision/latest?cb=20200311025301\" class=\"mw-file-description image\"><img alt=\"MG Unicorn Gundam Perfectibility\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"100\" height=\"54\" class=\"mw-file-element lazyload\" data-image-name=\"MG Unicorn Gundam Perfectibility.jpg\" data-image-key=\"MG_Unicorn_Gundam_Perfectibility.jpg\" data-relevant=\"1\" data-src=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/gundam/images/e/e4/MG_Unicorn_Gundam_Perfectibility.jpg/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/100?cb=20200311025301\" /></a><figcaption></figcaption></figure>\n</td>\n<td>The Gundam Base Limited <a href=\"/wiki/RX-0_Full_Armor_Unicorn_Gundam_Plan_B\" title=\"RX-0 Full Armor Unicorn Gundam Plan B\">Unicorn Gundam Perfectibility</a>\n</td>\n<td><i><a href=\"/wiki/Mobile_Suit_Gundam_UC_Perfectibility\" title=\"Mobile Suit Gundam UC Perfectibility\">Mobile Suit Gundam UC Perfectibility</a></i>\n</td>\n<td>\u00a512,000\n</td>\n<td>2019 July\n</td>\n<td>The Gundam Base exclusive parts variant of MG-131 with blue Psycho-Frame. Includes new tail stabilizers for Armed Armor DE units and extra <a href=\"/wiki/Banagher_Links\" title=\"Banagher Links\">Banagher Links</a> and <a href=\"/wiki/Marida_Cruz\" title=\"Marida Cruz\">Marida Cruz</a> figurines. Uses the BA, BD, and BF1 plate runners of MG-155, the WC and X plate runners of MG-150, and the WG2 plate runner of MG-179, as well as duplicate C and R1 plate runners for color accuracy.\n</td>\n<td>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>N/A <figure class=\"mw-halign-right\" typeof=\"mw:File\"><a href=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/gundam/images/e/e9/MG_F91_Gundam_F91_Ver.2.0_ORIGINAL_PLAN_Ver.jpg/revision/latest?cb=20190617063039\" class=\"mw-file-description image\"><img alt=\"MG F91 Gundam F91 Ver.2.0 ORIGINAL PLAN Ver\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D\" decoding=\"async\" loa