r variant of MG-207. Includes water slide decal sheet.\n</td>\n<td>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>N/A <figure class=\"mw-halign-right\" typeof=\"mw:File\"><a href=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/gundam/images/e/eb/MG_Dwadge_Custom.jpg/revision/latest?cb=20191123094136\" class=\"mw-file-description image\"><img alt=\"MG Dwadge Custom\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"100\" height=\"126\" class=\"mw-file-element lazyload\" data-image-name=\"MG Dwadge Custom.jpg\" data-image-key=\"MG_Dwadge_Custom.jpg\" data-relevant=\"1\" data-src=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/gundam/images/e/eb/MG_Dwadge_Custom.jpg/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/100?cb=20191123094136\" /></a><figcaption></figcaption></figure>\n</td>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/MS-09H_Dwadge_Custom\" title=\"MS-09H Dwadge Custom\">MS-09H Dwadge Custom</a>\n</td>\n<td><i><a href=\"/wiki/Mobile_Suit_Gundam_ZZ\" title=\"Mobile Suit Gundam ZZ\">Mobile Suit Gundam ZZ</a></i>\n</td>\n<td>\u00a55,500\n</td>\n<td>2019 November\n</td>\n<td>P-Bandai exclusive parts and color variant of MG <a href=\"/wiki/MS-09G_Dwadge\" title=\"MS-09G Dwadge\">MS-09G Dwadge</a>. Uses Emotion Manipulator SP (MP2) plate runner. Includes water slide decal sheet.\n</td>\n<td>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>N/A <figure class=\"mw-halign-right\" typeof=\"mw:File\"><a href=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/gundam/images/e/e0/MG_Mission_Pack_F-Type_%26_M-Type.jpg/revision/latest?cb=20191129034150\" class=\"mw-file-description image\"><img alt=\"MG Mission Pack F-Type &amp; M-Type\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"100\" height=\"156\" class=\"mw-file-element lazyload\" data-image-name=\"MG Mission Pack F-Type &amp; M-Type.jpg\" data-image-key=\"MG_Mission_Pack_F-Type_%26_M-Type.jpg\" data-relevant=\"1\" data-src=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/gundam/images/e/e0/MG_Mission_Pack_F-Type_%26_M-Type.jpg/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/100?cb=20191129034150\" /></a><figcaption></figcaption></figure>\n</td>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/Mission_Packs\" title=\"Mission Packs\">Mission Pack</a> <a href=\"/wiki/F90F_Gundam_F90_Fight_Type\" title=\"F90F Gundam F90 Fight Type\">F-Type</a> &amp; <a href=\"/wiki/F90M_Gundam_F90_Marine_Type\" title=\"F90M Gundam F90 Marine Type\">M-Type</a> for <a href=\"/wiki/F90_Gundam_F90\" title=\"F90 Gundam F90\">Gundam F90</a>\n</td>\n<td><i><a href=\"/wiki/Mobile_Suit_Gundam_F90\" title=\"Mobile Suit Gundam F90\">Mobile Suit Gundam F90</a></i>\n</td>\n<td>\u00a52,000\n</td>\n<td>2019 November\n</td>\n<td>P-Bandai exclusive accessory kit to convert MG F90 Gundam F90 into F90F Gundam F90 Fight Type or F90M Gundam F90 Marine Type; also compatible with MG <a href=\"/wiki/F90II_Gundam_F90II\" title=\"F90II Gundam F90II\">F90II Gundam F90II</a>. Includes water slide decal sheet. Released as part of P-Bandai's <a href=\"/wiki/F90_A_to_Z_PROJECT\" title=\"F90 A to Z PROJECT\">F90 A to Z Project</a> to coincide with the 10th anniversary of P-Bandai.\n</td>\n<td>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>N/A <figure class=\"mw-halign-right\" typeof=\"mw:File\"><a href=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/gundam/images/0/01/MG_Re-GZ_%28Unicorn_Ver.%29.jpg/revision/latest?cb=20191228061959\" class=\"mw-file-description image\"><img alt=\"MG Re-GZ (Unicorn Ver.)\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"100\" height=\"126\" class=\"mw-file-element lazyload\" data-image-name=\"MG Re-GZ (Unicorn Ver.).jpg\" data-image-key=\"MG_Re-GZ_%28Unicorn_Ver.%29.jpg\" data-relevant=\"1\" data-src=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/gundam/images/0/01/MG_Re-GZ_%28Unicorn_Ver.%29.jpg/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/100?cb=20191228061959\" /></a><figcaption></figcaption></figure>\n</td>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/RGZ-91_Re-GZ\" title=\"RGZ-91 Re-GZ\">RGZ-91 Re-GZ (Unicorn Ver.)</a>\n</td>\n<td><i><a href=\"/wiki/Mobile_Suit_Gundam_Unicorn\" title=\"Mobile Suit Gundam Unicorn\">Mobile Suit Gundam Unicorn</a></i>\n</td>\n<td>\u00a55,300\n</td>\n<td>2019 December\n</td>\n<td>P-Bandai exclusive parts and color variant of MG-039, with torso and hip inner frames revised to improve articulation. Includes water slide decal sheet. Fully transformable kit.\n</td>\n<td>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>N/A <figure class=\"mw-halign-right\" typeof=\"mw:File\"><a href=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/gundam/images/4/4d/MG_Jesta_Cannon_-Clear_Color-.jpg/revision/latest?cb=20191228154522\" class=\"mw-file-description image\"><img alt=\"MG Jesta Cannon -Clear Color-\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"100\" height=\"126\" class=\"mw-file-element lazyload\" data-image-name=\"MG Jesta Cannon -Clear Color-.jpg\" data-image-key=\"MG_Jesta_Cannon_-Clear_Color-.jpg\" data-relevant=\"1\" data-src=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/gundam/images/4/4d/MG_Jesta_Cannon_-Clear_Color-.jpg/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/100?cb=20191228154522\" /></a><figcaption></figcaption></figure>\n</td>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/RGM-96X_Jesta_Cannon\" title=\"RGM-96X Jesta Cannon\">RGM-96X Jesta Cannon</a> [Clear Color]\n</td>\n<td><i><a href=\"/wiki/Mobile_Suit_Gundam_Unicorn\" title=\"Mobile Suit Gundam Unicorn\">Mobile Suit Gundam Unicorn</a></i>\n</td>\n<td>\u00a55,000\n</td>\n<td>2019 December\n</td>\n<td>Events and The Gundam Base exclusive clear color variant of MG RGM-96X Jesta Cannon.\n</td>\n<td>\n</td></tr></tbody></table><p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p></div><div class=\"wds-tab__content\"><p class=\"mw-empty-elt\">\n</p><table class=\"wikitable sortable\">\n<tbody><tr>\n<th>MG #\n</th>\n<th>Model\n</th>\n<th>Series\n</th>\n<th>Yen Price\n</th>\n<th>Release Date\n</th>\n<th>Notes\n</th>\n<th>Link\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>N/A <figure class=\"mw-halign-right\" typeof=\"mw:File\"><a href=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/gundam/images/1/1d/MG_Tallgeese_III_-Special_Coating-.jpeg/revision/latest?cb=20200121161521\" class=\"mw-file-description image\"><img alt=\"MG Tallgeese III -Special Coating-\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"100\" height=\"79\" class=\"mw-file-element lazyload\" data-image-name=\"MG Tallgeese III -Special Coating-.jpeg\" data-image-key=\"MG_Tallgeese_III_-Special_Coating-.jpeg\" data-relevant=\"1\" data-src=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/gundam/images/1/1d/MG_Tallgeese_III_-Special_Coating-.jpeg/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/100?cb=20200121161521\" /></a><figcaption></figcaption></figure>\n</td>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/OZ-00MS2B_Tallgeese_III\" title=\"OZ-00MS2B Tallgeese III\">OZ-00MS2B Tallgeese III</a> [Special Coating]\n</td>\n<td><i><a href=\"/wiki/New_Mobile_Report_Gundam_Wing:_Endless_Waltz\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"New Mobile Report Gundam Wing: Endless Waltz\">New Mobile Report Gundam Wing: Endless Waltz</a></i>\n</td>\n<td>\u00a59,200\n</td>\n<td>2020 January\n</td>\n<td>Events and The Gundam Base exclusive parts and color variant of MG-164. Metallic color variant of MG OZ-00MS2B Tallgeese III. Includes water slide decal sheet.\n</td>\n<td>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>N/A <figure class=\"mw-halign-right\" typeof=\"mw:File\"><a href=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/gundam/images/8/82/MG_Blast_Impulse_Gundam.jpg/revision/latest?cb=20200121062316\" class=\"mw-file-description image\"><img alt=\"MG Blast Impulse Gundam\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"100\" height=\"80\" class=\"mw-file-element lazyload\" data-image-name=\"MG Blast Impulse Gundam.jpg\" data-image-key=\"MG_Blast_Impulse_Gundam.jpg\" data-relevant=\"1\" data-src=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/gundam/images/8/82/MG_Blast_Impulse_Gundam.jpg/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/100?cb=20200121062316\" /></a><figcaption></figcaption></figure>\n</td>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/ZGMF-X56S/%CE%B3_Blast_Impulse_Gundam\" title=\"ZGMF-X56S/\u03b3 Blast Impulse Gundam\">ZGMF-X56S/\u03b3 Blast Impulse Gundam</a>\n</td>\n<td><i><a href=\"/wiki/Mobile_Suit_Gundam_SEED_Destiny\" title=\"Mobile Suit Gundam SEED Destiny\">Mobile Suit Gundam SEED Destiny</a></i>\n</td>\n<td>\u00a55,000\n</td>\n<td>2020 January\n</td>\n<td>P-Bandai exclusive color variant of MG-109 with \u03b3 Blast Silhouette pack. Includes water slide decal sheet. Released to coincide with the 10th anniversary of P-Bandai.\n</td>\n<td>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>N/A <figure class=\"mw-halign-right\" typeof=\"mw:File\"><a href=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/gundam/images/a/a1/MG_Mission_Pack_B-Type_%26_K-Type.jpg/revision/latest?cb=20200318143721\" class=\"mw-file-description image\"><img alt=\"MG Mission Pack B-Type &amp; K-Type\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"100\" height=\"155\" class=\"mw-file-element lazyload\" data-image-name=\"MG Mission Pack B-Type &amp; K-Type.jpg\" data-image-key=\"MG_Mission_Pack_B-Type_%26_K-Type.jpg\" data-relevant=\"1\" data-src=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/gundam/images/a/a1/MG_Mission_Pack_B-Type_%26_K-Type.jpg/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/100?cb=20200318143721\" /></a><figcaption></figcaption></figure>\n</td>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/Mission_Packs\" title=\"Mission Packs\">Mission Pack</a> <a href=\"/wiki/F90B_Gundam_F90_Bombard_Type\" title=\"F90B Gundam F90 Bombard Type\">B-Type</a> &amp; <a href=\"/wiki/F90K_Gundam_F90_Keep_Type\" title=\"F90K Gundam F90 Keep Type\">K-Type</a> for <a href=\"/wiki/F90_Gundam_F90\" title=\"F90 Gundam F90\">Gundam F90</a>\n</td>\n<td><i><a href=\"/wiki/Mobile_Suit_Gundam_F90\" title=\"Mobile Suit Gundam F90\">Mobile Suit Gundam F90</a></i>\n</td>\n<td>\u00a52,000\n</td>\n<td>2020 March\n</td>\n<td>P-Bandai exclusive accessory kit to convert MG F90 Gundam F90 into F90B Gundam F90 Bombard Type or F90K Gundam F90 Endurance (Keep) Type; also compatible with MG <a href=\"/wiki/F90II_Gundam_F90II\" title=\"F90II Gundam F90II\">F90II Gundam F90II</a>. Includes water slide decal sheet. Released as part of P-Bandai's <a href=\"/wiki/F90_A_to_Z_PROJECT\" title=\"F90 A to Z PROJECT\">F90 A to Z Project</a> to coincide with the 10th anniversary of P-Bandai.\n</td>\n<td>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>N/A <figure class=\"mw-halign-right\" typeof=\"mw:File\"><a href=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/gundam/images/0/07/MG_Zaku_II_Ver.LUNA_SEA.jpg/revision/latest?cb=20200131095043\" class=\"mw-file-description image\"><img alt=\"MG Zaku II Ver.LUNA SEA\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"100\" height=\"119\" class=\"mw-file-element lazyload\" data-image-name=\"MG Zaku II Ver.LUNA SEA.jpg\" data-image-key=\"MG_Zaku_II_Ver.LUNA_SEA.jpg\" data-relevant=\"1\" data-src=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/gundam/images/0/07/MG_Zaku_II_Ver.LUNA_SEA.jpg/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/100?cb=20200131095043\" /></a><figcaption></figcaption></figure>\n</td>\n<td>THE BEYOND GUNPLA 40th EDITION THE BEYOND x <a href=\"/wiki/MS-06S_Zaku_II_Commander_Type\" title=\"MS-06S Zaku II Commander Type\">MS-06LS Zaku II Ver.LUNA SEA</a>\n</td>\n<td><i><a href=\"/wiki/Mobile_Suit_Gundam\" title=\"Mobile Suit Gundam\">Mobile Suit Gundam</a></i>\n</td>\n<td>\u00a56,000\n</td>\n<td>2020 April\n</td>\n<td>Universal Music Japan exclusive color variant of MG-098; bundled with CD of Luna Sea's single <i>THE BEYOND</i>. Released as part of the Gunpla 40th anniversary \u00d7 LUNA SEA 30th anniversary celebration, and to commemorate the release of the new single, which is the theme song of Gundam 40th anniversary celebration. This is an Ecopla kit, meaning it uses recycled excess plastic materials that were rejected from the factory.\n</td>\n<td>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>N/A <figure class=\"mw-halign-right\" typeof=\"mw:File\"><a href=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/gundam/images/4/4e/MG_Slash_ZAKU_Phantom_%28Yzak_Jule_Custom%29.jpg/revision/latest?cb=20200419081358\" class=\"mw-file-description image\"><img alt=\"MG Slash ZAKU Phantom (Yzak Jule Custom)\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"100\" height=\"81\" class=\"mw-file-element lazyload\" data-image-name=\"MG Slash ZAKU Phantom (Yzak Jule Custom).jpg\" data-image-key=\"MG_Slash_ZAKU_Phantom_%28Yzak_Jule_Custom%29.jpg\" data-relevant=\"1\" data-src=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/gundam/images/4/4e/MG_Slash_ZAKU_Phantom_%28Yzak_Jule_Custom%29.jpg/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/100?cb=20200419081358\" /></a><figcaption></figcaption></figure>\n</td>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/ZGMF-1001/K_Slash_ZAKU_Phantom\" title=\"ZGMF-1001/K Slash ZAKU Phantom\">ZGMF-1001/K Slash ZAKU Phantom (Yzak Jule Custom)</a>\n</td>\n<td><i><a href=\"/wiki/Mobile_Suit_Gundam_SEED_Destiny\" title=\"Mobile Suit Gundam SEED Destiny\">Mobile Suit Gundam SEED Destiny</a></i>\n</td>\n<td>\u00a54,500\n</td>\n<td>2020 April\n</td>\n<td>P-Bandai exclusive parts and color variant of MG-211. Includes water slide decal sheet.\n</td>\n<td>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>N/A <figure class=\"mw-halign-right\" typeof=\"mw:File\"><a href=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/gundam/images/c/c9/MG_Gundam_Deathscythe_EW_%28Roussette_Unit%29.jpg/revision/latest?cb=20200419081350\" class=\"mw-file-description image\"><img alt=\"MG Gundam Deathscythe EW (Roussette Unit)\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"100\" height=\"155\" class=\"mw-file-element lazyload\" data-image-name=\"MG Gundam Deathscythe EW (Roussette Unit).jpg\" data-image-key=\"MG_Gundam_Deathscythe_EW_%28Roussette_Unit%29.jpg\" data-relevant=\"1\" data-src=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/gundam/images/c/c9/MG_Gundam_Deathscythe_EW_%28Roussette_Unit%29.jpg/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/100?cb=20200419081350\" /></a><figcaption></figcaption></figure>\n</td>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/XXXG-01D_Gundam_Deathscythe_EW\" title=\"XXXG-01D Gundam Deathscythe EW\">XXXG-01D Gundam Deathscythe EW (Roussette Unit)</a>\n</td>\n<td><i><a href=\"/wiki/New_Mobile_Report_Gundam_Wing_Endless_Waltz:_The_Glory_of_Losers\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"New Mobile Report Gundam Wing Endless Waltz: The Glory of Losers\">New Mobile Report Gundam Wing Endless Waltz: The Glory of Losers</a></i>\n</td>\n<td>\u00a54,500\n</td>\n<td>2020 April\n</td>\n<td>P-Bandai exclusive re-release of MG-138 with Roussette Unit. Includes water slide decal sheet.\n</td>\n<td>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>N/A <figure class=\"mw-halign-right\" typeof=\"mw:File\"><a href=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/gundam/images/8/83/MG_Victory_Two_Assault_Buster_Gundam_Ver.Ka_-Titanium_Finish-.jpg/revision/latest?cb=20200416030931\" class=\"mw-file-description image\"><img alt=\"MG Victory Two Assault Buster Gundam Ver.Ka -Titanium Finish-\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"100\" height=\"126\" class=\"mw-file-element lazyload\" data-image-name=\"MG Victory Two Assault Buster Gundam Ver.Ka -Titanium Finish-.jpg\" data-image-key=\"MG_Victory_Two_Assault_Buster_Gundam_Ver.Ka_-Titanium_Finish-.jpg\" data-relevant=\"1\" data-src=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/gundam/images/8/83/MG_Victory_Two_Assault_Buster_Gundam_Ver.Ka_-Titanium_Finish-.jpg/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/100?cb=20200416030931\" /></a><figcaption></figcaption></figure>\n</td>\n<td>The Gundam Base Limited <a href=\"/wiki/LM314V23/24_V2_Assault-Buster_Gundam\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"LM314V23/24 V2 Assault-Buster Gundam\">Victory Two Assault Buster Gundam \"Ver.Ka\"</a> [Titanium Finish]\n</td>\n<td><i><a href=\"/wiki/Mobile_Suit_Victory_Gundam\" title=\"Mobile Suit Victory Gundam\">Mobile Suit Victory Gundam</a></i>\n</td>\n<td>\u00a515,000\n</td>\n<td>2020 May\n</td>\n<td>The Gundam Base exclusive metallic color variant of MG LM314V23/24 Victory Two Assault Buster Gundam \"Ver.Ka\". Originally planned to be released in April 2020, but was delayed given The Gundam Base's temporary closure due to COVID-19.<sup id=\"cite_ref-COVID19_GBT_1_17-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-COVID19_GBT_1-17\"><span class=\"cite-bracket\">&#91;</span>17<span class=\"cite-bracket\">&#93;</span></a></sup>\n</td>\n<td>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>N/A <figure class=\"mw-halign-right\" typeof=\"mw:File\"><a href=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/gundam/images/f/fe/MG_Gundam_Barbatos_-Clear_Color-.jpg/revision/latest?cb=20200608110057\" class=\"mw-file-description image\"><img alt=\"MG Gundam Barbatos -Clear Color-\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"100\" height=\"126\" class=\"mw-file-element lazyload\" data-image-name=\"MG Gundam Barbatos -Clear Color-.jpg\" data-image-key=\"MG_Gundam_Barbatos_-Clear_Color-.jpg\" data-relevant=\"1\" data-src=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/gundam/images/f/fe/MG_Gundam_Barbatos_-Clear_Color-.jpg/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/100?cb=20200608110057\" /></a><figcaption></figcaption></figure>\n</td>\n<td>The Gundam Base Limited <a href=\"/wiki/ASW-G-08_Gundam_Barbatos\" title=\"ASW-G-08 Gundam Barbatos\">Gundam Barbatos</a> [Clear Color]\n</td>\n<td><i><a href=\"/wiki/Mobile_Suit_Gundam_IRON-BLOODED_ORPHANS\" title=\"Mobile Suit Gundam IRON-BLOODED ORPHANS\">Mobile Suit Gundam IRON-BLOODED ORPHANS</a></i>\n</td>\n<td>\u00a54,500\n</td>\n<td>2020 June\n</td>\n<td>The Gundam Base exclusive clear color variant of MG-212.\n</td>\n<td>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>N/A <figure class=\"mw-halign-right\" typeof=\"mw:File\"><a href=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/gundam/images/c/c6/MG_Catapult_Base.jpg/revision/latest?cb=20200608110045\" class=\"mw-file-description image\"><img alt=\"MG Catapult Base\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"100\" height=\"57\" class=\"mw-file-element lazyload\" data-image-name=\"MG Catapult Base.jpg\" data-image-key=\"MG_Catapult_Base.jpg\" data-relevant=\"1\" data-src=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/gundam/images/c/c6/MG_Catapult_Base.jpg/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/100?cb=20200608110045\" /></a><figcaption></figcaption></figure>\n</td>\n<td>The Gundam Base Limited Catapult Base\n</td>\n<td><i><a href=\"/wiki/Mobile_Suit_Zeta_Gundam\" title=\"Mobile Suit Zeta Gundam\">Mobile Suit Zeta Gundam</a></i>\n</td>\n<td>\u00a52,300\n</td>\n<td>2020 June\n</td>\n<td>The Gundam Base exclusive accessory kit. Catapult uses bases previously released in MG-082 and MG-083. Includes a new 1/100 scale human crew runner.\n</td>\n<td>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>N/A <figure class=\"mw-halign-right\" typeof=\"mw:File\"><a href=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/gundam/images/a/ac/MG_Jegan_D_Type_%28First_Deployment_Type%29.jpg/revision/latest?cb=20200617010115\" class=\"mw-file-description image\"><img alt=\"MG Jegan D Type (First Deployment Type)\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"100\" height=\"126\" class=\"mw-file-element lazyload\" data-image-name=\"MG Jegan D Type (First Deployment Type).jpg\" data-image-key=\"MG_Jegan_D_Type_%28First_Deployment_Type%29.jpg\" data-relevant=\"1\" data-src=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/gundam/images/a/ac/MG_Jegan_D_Type_%28First_Deployment_Type%29.jpg/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/100?cb=20200617010115\" /></a><figcaption></figcaption></figure>\n</td>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/RGM-89D_Jegan_D_Type\" title=\"RGM-89D Jegan D Type\">RGM-89D Jegan D Type (First Deployment Type)</a>\n</td>\n<td><i><a href=\"/wiki/UC-MSV\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"UC-MSV\">Mobile Suit Gundam Unicorn MSV</a></i>\n</td>\n<td>\u00a54,200\n</td>\n<td>2020 June\n</td>\n<td>P-Bandai exclusive color variant of MG <a href=\"/wiki/RGM-89D_Jegan_D_Type\" title=\"RGM-89D Jegan D Type\">RGM-89D Jegan D Type</a>. Includes water slide decal sheet.\n</td>\n<td>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>N/A <figure class=\"mw-halign-right\" typeof=\"mw:File\"><a href=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/gundam/images/d/d1/MG_Gundam_F90II_I-Type.jpg/revision/latest?cb=20200904043222\" class=\"mw-file-description image\"><img alt=\"MG Gundam F90II I-Type\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"100\" height=\"126\" class=\"mw-file-element lazyload\" data-image-name=\"MG Gundam F90II I-Type.jpg\" data-image-key=\"MG_Gundam_F90II_I-Type.jpg\" data-relevant=\"1\" data-src=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/gundam/images/d/d1/MG_Gundam_F90II_I-Type.jpg/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/100?cb=20200904043222\" /></a><figcaption></figcaption></figure>\n</td>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/F90II-I_Gundam_F90II_Intercept_Type\" title=\"F90II-I Gundam F90II Intercept Type\">F90II-I Gundam F90II I-Type</a>\n</td>\n<td><i><a href=\"/wiki/Mobile_Suit_Gundam_F90\" title=\"Mobile Suit Gundam F90\">Mobile Suit Gundam F90</a></i>\n</td>\n<td>\u00a56,000\n</td>\n<td>2020 July\n</td>\n<td>P-Bandai exclusive parts and color variant of MG <a href=\"/wiki/F90_Gundam_F90\" title=\"F90 Gundam F90\">F90 Gundam F90</a>; I-Type equipments also compatible with MG F90 Gundam F90. Includes support stand for Flight Shield and water slide decal sheet. Released as part of P-Bandai's <a href=\"/wiki/F90_A_to_Z_PROJECT\" title=\"F90 A to Z PROJECT\">F90 A to Z Project</a>.\n</td>\n<td>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>N/A <figure class=\"mw-halign-right\" typeof=\"mw:File\"><a href=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/gundam/images/0/0a/MG_FAZZ_Ver.Ka_-Titanium_Finish-.jpg/revision/latest?cb=20201209235716\" class=\"mw-file-description image\"><img alt=\"MG FAZZ Ver.Ka -Titanium Finish-\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"100\" height=\"68\" class=\"mw-file-element lazyload\" data-image-name=\"MG FAZZ Ver.Ka -Titanium Finish-.jpg\" data-image-key=\"MG_FAZZ_Ver.Ka_-Titanium_Finish-.jpg\" data-relevant=\"1\" data-src=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/gundam/images/0/0a/MG_FAZZ_Ver.Ka_-Titanium_Finish-.jpg/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/100?cb=20201209235716\" /></a><figcaption></figcaption></figure>\n</td>\n<td>The Gundam Base Limited <a href=\"/wiki/FA-010A_FAZZ\" title=\"FA-010A FAZZ\">FAZZ \"Ver.Ka\"</a> [Titanium Finish]\n</td>\n<td><i><a href=\"/wiki/Gundam_Sentinel\" title=\"Gundam Sentinel\">Gundam Sentinel</a></i>\n</td>\n<td>\u00a522,000\n</td>\n<td>2020 August\n</td>\n<td>The Gundam Base exclusive metallic color variant of MG-213.\n</td>\n<td>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>N/A <figure class=\"mw-halign-right\" typeof=\"mw:File\"><a href=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/gundam/images/9/93/MG_Gundam_Astray_Red_Frame_Flight_Unit.jpg/revision/latest?cb=20200823034814\" class=\"mw-file-description image\"><img alt=\"MG Gundam Astray Red Frame Flight Unit\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"100\" height=\"80\" class=\"mw-file-element lazyload\" data-image-name=\"MG Gundam Astray Red Frame Flight Unit.jpg\" data-image-key=\"MG_Gundam_Astray_Red_Frame_Flight_Unit.jpg\" data-relevant=\"1\" data-src=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/gundam/images/9/93/MG_Gundam_Astray_Red_Frame_Flight_Unit.jpg/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/100?cb=20200823034814\" /></a><figcaption></figcaption></figure>\n</td>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/MBF-P02_Gundam_Astray_Red_Frame\" title=\"MBF-P02 Gundam Astray Red Frame\">MBF-P02 Gundam Astray Red Frame Flight Unit</a>\n</td>\n<td><i><a href=\"/wiki/Mobile_Suit_Gundam_SEED_Destiny_Astray_R\" title=\"Mobile Suit Gundam SEED Destiny Astray R\">Mobile Suit Gundam SEED Destiny Astray R</a></i>\n</td>\n<td>\u00a56,500\n</td>\n<td>2020 August\n</td>\n<td>P-Bandai exclusive re-release of MG <a href=\"/wiki/MBF-P02_Gundam_Astray_Red_Frame\" title=\"MBF-P02 Gundam Astray Red Frame\">MBF-P02 Gundam Astray Red Frame</a> with Flight Unit and BuCUE Tactical Reconnaissance Type Head unit. Includes water slide decal sheet.\n</td>\n<td>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>N/A <figure class=\"mw-halign-right\" typeof=\"mw:File\"><a href=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/gundam/images/4/4c/MG_Flight_Unit_Expansion_Set_for_Gundam_Astray_Red_Frame.jpg/revision/latest?cb=20200823034824\" class=\"mw-file-description image\"><img alt=\"MG Flight Unit Expansion Set for Gundam Astray Red Frame\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"100\" height=\"65\" class=\"mw-file-element lazyload\" data-image-name=\"MG Flight Unit Expansion Set for Gundam Astray Red Frame.jpg\" data-image-key=\"MG_Flight_Unit_Expansion_Set_for_Gundam_Astray_Red_Frame.jpg\" data-relevant=\"1\" data-src=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/gundam/images/4/4c/MG_Flight_Unit_Expansion_Set_for_Gundam_Astray_Red_Frame.jpg/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/100?cb=20200823034824\" /></a><figcaption></figcaption></figure>\n</td>\n<td>Flight Unit Expansion Set for <a href=\"/wiki/MBF-P02_Gundam_Astray_Red_Frame\" title=\"MBF-P02 Gundam Astray Red Frame\">Gundam Astray Red Frame</a>\n</td>\n<td><i><a href=\"/wiki/Mobile_Suit_Gundam_SEED_Destiny_Astray_R\" title=\"Mobile Suit Gundam SEED Destiny Astray R\">Mobile Suit Gundam SEED Destiny Astray R</a></i>\n</td>\n<td>\u00a52,000\n</td>\n<td>2020 August\n</td>\n<td>P-Bandai exclusive accessory kit to convert MG MBF-P02 Gundam Astray Red Frame into <a href=\"/wiki/MBF-P02_Gundam_Astray_Red_Frame\" title=\"MBF-P02 Gundam Astray Red Frame\">MBF-P02 Gundam Astray Red Frame Flight Unit</a>. Includes water slide decal sheet.\n</td>\n<td>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>N/A <figure class=\"mw-halign-right\" typeof=\"mw:File\"><a href=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/gundam/images/4/4c/MG_Qubeley_Embellir.jpg/revision/latest?cb=20200822081712\" class=\"mw-file-description image\"><img alt=\"MG Qubeley Embellir\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"100\" height=\"78\" class=\"mw-file-element lazyload\" data-image-name=\"MG Qubeley Embellir.jpg\" data-image-key=\"MG_Qubeley_Embellir.jpg\" data-relevant=\"1\" data-src=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/gundam/images/4/4c/MG_Qubeley_Embellir.jpg/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/100?cb=20200822081712\" /></a><figcaption></figcaption></figure>\n</td>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/AMX-004DMD_Qubeley_Damned#Variants\" title=\"AMX-004DMD Qubeley Damned\">Qubeley Embellir</a>\n</td>\n<td><i><a href=\"/wiki/Gundam_Build_Divers_GBWC\" title=\"Gundam Build Divers GBWC\">Gundam Build Divers GBWC</a></i>\n</td>\n<td>\u00a55,400\n</td>\n<td>2020 August\n</td>\n<td>P-Bandai exclusive gloss color variant of MG <a href=\"/wiki/AMX-004DMD_Qubeley_Damned\" title=\"AMX-004DMD Qubeley Damned\">AMX-004DMD Qubeley Damned</a>. Includes water slide decal sheet.\n</td>\n<td>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>N/A <figure class=\"mw-halign-right\" typeof=\"mw:File\"><a href=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/gundam/images/5/5d/MG_GM_II_%28A.E.U.G._Color_Ver.%29.jpg/revision/latest?cb=20200924010647\" class=\"mw-file-description image\"><img alt=\"MG GM II (A.E.U.G. Color Ver.)\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEA