e for Gundam F90.jpg\" data-image-key=\"Mission_Pack_A-Type_%26_L-Type_for_Gundam_F90.jpg\" data-relevant=\"1\" data-src=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/gundam/images/a/ab/Mission_Pack_A-Type_%26_L-Type_for_Gundam_F90.jpg/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/100?cb=20240701062242\" /></a><figcaption></figcaption></figure>\n</td>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/Mission_Packs\" title=\"Mission Packs\">Mission Pack</a> <a href=\"/wiki/F90A_Gundam_F90_Assault_Type\" title=\"F90A Gundam F90 Assault Type\">A-Type</a> &amp; <a href=\"/wiki/F90II-L_Gundam_F90II_Long_Range_Type\" title=\"F90II-L Gundam F90II Long Range Type\">L-Type</a> for <a href=\"/wiki/F90_Gundam_F90\" title=\"F90 Gundam F90\">Gundam F90</a>\n</td>\n<td><i><a href=\"/wiki/Mobile_Suit_Gundam_F90\" title=\"Mobile Suit Gundam F90\">Mobile Suit Gundam F90</a></i>\n</td>\n<td>\u00a52,500\n</td>\n<td>2024 February\n</td>\n<td>P-Bandai exclusive accessory kit to convert MG F90 Gundam F90 into F90A Gundam F90 Assault Type and MG <a href=\"/wiki/F90II-I_Gundam_F90II_Intercept_Type\" title=\"F90II-I Gundam F90II Intercept Type\">F90II-I Gundam F90II Intercept Type</a> into F90II-L Gundam F90II Long Range Type; also interchangeably compatible. Includes water slide decal sheet. Released as part of P-Bandai's <a href=\"/wiki/F90_A_to_Z_PROJECT\" title=\"F90 A to Z PROJECT\">F90 A to Z Project</a>.\n</td>\n<td>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>N/A <figure class=\"mw-halign-right\" typeof=\"mw:File\"><a href=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/gundam/images/3/3f/GAT-X303_Aegis_Gundam_%28Clear_Color%29.jpg/revision/latest?cb=20240701072045\" class=\"mw-file-description image\"><img alt=\"GAT-X303 Aegis Gundam (Clear Color)\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"100\" height=\"81\" class=\"mw-file-element lazyload\" data-image-name=\"GAT-X303 Aegis Gundam (Clear Color).jpg\" data-image-key=\"GAT-X303_Aegis_Gundam_%28Clear_Color%29.jpg\" data-relevant=\"1\" data-src=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/gundam/images/3/3f/GAT-X303_Aegis_Gundam_%28Clear_Color%29.jpg/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/100?cb=20240701072045\" /></a><figcaption></figcaption></figure>\n</td>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/GAT-X303_Aegis_Gundam\" title=\"GAT-X303 Aegis Gundam\">GAT-X303 Aegis Gundam</a> [Clear Color]\n</td>\n<td><i><a href=\"/wiki/Mobile_Suit_Gundam_SEED\" title=\"Mobile Suit Gundam SEED\">Mobile Suit Gundam SEED</a></i>\n</td>\n<td>\u00a55,100\n</td>\n<td>2024 March\n</td>\n<td>Events and The Gundam Base exclusive clear color variant of MG-161.\n</td>\n<td>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>N/A <figure class=\"mw-halign-right\" typeof=\"mw:File\"><a href=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/gundam/images/e/ec/ZGMF-1017_Mobile_Ginn_%28Miguel_Aiman_Custom%29.jpg/revision/latest?cb=20240701072221\" class=\"mw-file-description image\"><img alt=\"ZGMF-1017 Mobile Ginn (Miguel Aiman Custom)\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"100\" height=\"80\" class=\"mw-file-element lazyload\" data-image-name=\"ZGMF-1017 Mobile Ginn (Miguel Aiman Custom).jpg\" data-image-key=\"ZGMF-1017_Mobile_Ginn_%28Miguel_Aiman_Custom%29.jpg\" data-relevant=\"1\" data-src=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/gundam/images/e/ec/ZGMF-1017_Mobile_Ginn_%28Miguel_Aiman_Custom%29.jpg/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/100?cb=20240701072221\" /></a><figcaption></figcaption></figure>\n</td>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/ZGMF-1017_Miguel%27s_GINN\" title=\"ZGMF-1017 Miguel&#39;s GINN\">ZGMF-1017 Mobile Ginn (Miguel Aiman Custom)</a>\n</td>\n<td><i><a href=\"/wiki/Mobile_Suit_Gundam_SEED_MSV\" title=\"Mobile Suit Gundam SEED MSV\">Mobile Suit Gundam SEED MSV</a></i>\n</td>\n<td>\u00a54,900\n</td>\n<td>2024 March\n</td>\n<td>P-Bandai and HYPER PLAMO Fes. 2024 exclusive color variant of MG-216 with Shield. Includes water slide decal sheet.\n</td>\n<td>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>N/A