 title=\"F90 A to Z PROJECT\">F90 A to Z Project</a>.\n</td>\n<td>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>N/A <figure class=\"mw-halign-right\" typeof=\"mw:File\"><a href=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/gundam/images/7/7b/MG_Gundam_Exia_Clear_Color.jpg/revision/latest?cb=20241012172422\" class=\"mw-file-description image\"><img alt=\"MG Gundam Exia Clear Color\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"100\" height=\"156\" class=\"mw-file-element lazyload\" data-image-name=\"MG Gundam Exia Clear Color.jpg\" data-image-key=\"MG_Gundam_Exia_Clear_Color.jpg\" data-relevant=\"1\" data-src=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/gundam/images/7/7b/MG_Gundam_Exia_Clear_Color.jpg/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/100?cb=20241012172422\" /></a><figcaption></figcaption></figure>\n</td>\n<td>The Gundam Base Limited <a href=\"/wiki/GN-001_Gundam_Exia\" title=\"GN-001 Gundam Exia\">Gundam Exia</a> [Clear Color]\n</td>\n<td><i><a href=\"/wiki/Mobile_Suit_Gundam_00\" title=\"Mobile Suit Gundam 00\">Mobile Suit Gundam 00</a></i>\n</td>\n<td>\u00a53,800\n</td>\n<td>2024 November\n</td>\n<td>The Gundam Base exclusive clear color variant of MG-123.\n</td>\n<td>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>N/A\n</td>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/RX-9/B_Narrative_Gundam_B-Packs\" title=\"RX-9/B Narrative Gundam B-Packs\">B-Packs</a> Expansion Set for <a href=\"/wiki/RX-9/C_Narrative_Gundam_C-Packs\" title=\"RX-9/C Narrative Gundam C-Packs\">Narrative Gundam C-Packs \"Ver.Ka\"</a>\n</td>\n<td><i><a href=\"/wiki/Mobile_Suit_Gundam_Narrative\" title=\"Mobile Suit Gundam Narrative\">Mobile Suit Gundam Narrative</a></i>\n</td>\n<td>\u00a52,600\n</td>\n<td>2024 November\n</td>\n<td>P-Bandai exclusive accessory kit to convert MG-222 into RX-9/B Narrative Gundam B-Packs. Includes backpack adapter part, adapted <a href=\"/wiki/High_Grade_the_Witch_from_Mercury\" title=\"High Grade the Witch from Mercury\">HGTWFM</a> Weapon Display Base to pose incoms, and water slide decal sheet.\n</td>\n<td>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>N/A\n</td>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/RX-9/B_Narrative_Gundam_B-Packs\" title=\"RX-9/B Narrative Gundam B-Packs\">RX-9/B Narrative Gundam B-Packs \"Ver.Ka\"</a>\n</td>\n<td><i><a href=\"/wiki/Mobile_Suit_Gundam_Narrative\" title=\"Mobile Suit Gundam Narrative\">Mobile Suit Gundam Narrative</a></i>\n</td>\n<td>\u00a59,500\n</td>\n<td>2024 November\n</td>\n<td>P-Bandai exclusive re-release of MG-222 with MG B-Packs Expansion Set for Narrative Gundam C-Packs \"Ver.Ka\". Replaces C plate runner with paintable clear Psycho-Frame parts. Includes white <a href=\"/wiki/Action_Base\" title=\"Action Base\">Action Base</a> 4.\n</td>\n<td>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>N/A <figure class=\"mw-halign-right\" typeof=\"mw:File\"><a href=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/gundam/images/b/b9/MG_Riko%27s_Zaku.png/revision/latest?cb=20240629222809\" class=\"mw-file-description image\"><img alt=\"MG Riko&#39;s Zaku\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"130\" height=\"106\" class=\"mw-file-element lazyload\" data-image-name=\"MG Riko&#39;s Zaku.png\" data-image-key=\"MG_Riko%27s_Zaku.png\" data-relevant=\"1\" data-src=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/gundam/images/b/b9/MG_Riko%27s_Zaku.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/130?cb=20240629222809\" /></a><figcaption></figcaption></figure>\n</td>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/MS-06_Zaku_II\" title=\"MS-06 Zaku II\">Riko's Zaku (Plastic Model and RIKO Ver.)</a>\n</td>\n<td><i>Plastic Model and RIKO: Puramo Joshi no Jinsei Kumitate ki</i>\n</td>\n<td>\u00a54,200\n</td>\n<td>2024 December\n</td>\n<td>P-Bandai exclusive color variant of MG-097. Includes special decal sheet.\n</td>\n<td>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>N/A\n</td>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/MBF-P02Kai_Gundam_Astray_Red_Frame_Kai\" title=\"MBF-P02Kai Gundam Astray Red Frame Kai\">MBF-P02Kai Gundam Astray Red Frame</a> [Cross Contrast C